Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:08.64,0:00:11.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,I'm a soldier 而那也就是說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:11.91,0:00:15.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是被告也是法官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:15.14,0:00:21.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我同時站在火線的兩端
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:21.85,0:00:28.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,繞過危險的轉角追過生與死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:28.26,0:00:33.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我奔向前挑戰謊言的影子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:34.06,0:00:40.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,無論編織出多少謊言
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:40.83,0:00:48.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真相還是會照出光明的輪廓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:48.88,0:00:50.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,留著你的眼淚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:50.44,0:00:51.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,給那一天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:52.01,0:00:55.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,當我們的痛苦都拋在腦後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:55.28,0:00:56.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,站起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:56.92,0:00:58.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跟著我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:58.55,0:01:01.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們是士兵不是站著就是死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:01.96,0:01:03.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,留著你的眼淚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:03.52,0:01:05.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,佔好你的位置
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:05.09,0:01:08.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把它們留給審判之日
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:08.43,0:01:09.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快速而且自由
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:10.06,0:01:11.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跟著我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:11.73,0:01:16.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,犧牲的時候到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:16.47,0:01:19.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們只能奮起或是倒地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:19.47,0:01:22.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,攻殼機動隊 S.A.C. 2nd GIG
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:33.35,0:01:36.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,偽裝成意外的他殺案件嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:36.26,0:01:37.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,根據調查員所述
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:37.82,0:01:43.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,撞的時候很可能故意對腦殼造成確實傷害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:43.53,0:01:48.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是卡車駕駛說他開車打瞌睡完全沒有記憶?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:48.74,0:01:51.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為求慎重起見我們正在清查駕駛的電子腦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:51.87,0:01:53.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過  恐怕不會有任何發現吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:54.27,0:01:59.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惜恐嚇能源省犯人的線索就這樣斷了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:59.85,0:02:02.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果這個男人是單獨犯的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:03.18,0:02:06.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,被害者的義體是豐田化工制2902型
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:07.02,0:02:10.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,腦殼是Dermo制2706型改良版
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:10.32,0:02:13.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖然型號落伍但兩者都是全新的國產機種
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:13.39,0:02:16.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,外表是市售的標準型式沒有附加額外功能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:16.80,0:02:18.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只有臉部是訂製的高級品
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:18.87,0:02:20.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過  從細胞老化的程度來看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:20.77,0:02:24.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,應該是從第一次義體化就用到現在了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:24.10,0:02:27.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以犯罪者來說這種換裝模式不太正常
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:27.67,0:02:31.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再加上恐嚇手法好像也很拙劣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:32.21,0:02:37.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有可能連能源省醜聞這個情報都只是故弄玄虛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:37.95,0:02:44.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是他卻在被逮捕的前一刻死在疑似暗殺的手法之下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:44.99,0:02:46.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個印記是什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.46,0:02:49.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好像是舊首都新宿區的標誌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.80,0:02:51.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在大戰中沉入水底?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:51.40,0:02:56.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個腦殼不知為何鍍了一層玻璃和鉛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.50,0:02:59.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好像是鍍的時候刻上去的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.91,0:03:02.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是男子身上的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.08,0:03:05.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,裏面有一個記者的聯絡方式
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:05.41,0:03:08.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,應該可以當作清查身份的線索
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:10.68,0:03:13.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這應該是結婚戒指吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:16.29,0:03:19.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,#06 潛在熱源
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.70,0:03:28.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們事務所的確有接到希望見面的聯絡電話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.34,0:03:29.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原來如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.17,0:03:33.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖然密告的內容十分可疑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.07,0:03:36.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過  電話好像是從東京的公用終端機打來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:36.68,0:03:37.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,東京?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.61,0:03:40.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼密告的內容是什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:40.48,0:03:43.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跟能源省有關的醜聞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:43.88,0:03:46.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要是一一確認這種密告
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.39,0:03:47.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們不就什麼事都做不了了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.02,0:03:50.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖然很少跟他實際碰面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.96,0:03:53.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過  他說要寄給我能夠證明這條新聞的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.10,0:03:56.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請問是兩位嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.66,0:03:58.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,兩位抽不抽煙呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.03,0:04:00.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請往這邊走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.14,0:04:06.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,黑漆漆的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.01,0:04:09.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大概是什麼能當證據的照片吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.81,0:04:11.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惜完全曝光了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.85,0:04:15.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他大概是認為數位資料沒有證據能力吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.15,0:04:18.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在很少人會使用底片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.39,0:04:20.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個可以交給我保管嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.89,0:04:23.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可以啊不過真的什麼都沒拍到喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.63,0:04:27.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,課長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.03,0:04:29.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看樣子這個男子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.46,0:04:30.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到被殺的前幾天為止
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.00,0:04:32.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好像都待在東京市內
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.93,0:04:36.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還從那邊把曝光的底片寄給記者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:36.97,0:04:37.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.87,0:04:40.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你就根據這條線索到東京去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.11,0:04:44.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這段期間我們會把他使用的終端機找出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.48,0:04:46.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只有我一個人去嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.55,0:04:50.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,其他人都還在繼續執行總理的貼身警衛工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.85,0:04:52.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我派一台塔奇克馬跟你去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:53.22,0:04:55.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,輻射方面已經沒問題了吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.62,0:04:58.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你以為大戰已經過去幾年了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.59,0:05:00.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,散佈「日本的奇跡」之後（一種能清除輻射的微機械）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.29,0:05:02.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就沒有再發現過殘留輻射
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.66,0:05:04.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,瞭解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.64,0:05:19.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,新東京  新東京到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.28,0:05:24.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在到站的列車是往Berutarube的擇捉3號
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.59,0:06:09.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果這麼在意殘留輻射我建議你去做義體化
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.56,0:06:11.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,才不是這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.60,0:06:13.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只是不知不覺就覺得
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:13.40,0:06:15.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,覺得不舒服嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.20,0:06:17.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那我可以讓你坐進駕駛艙喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.87,0:06:19.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那可能會讓我暈車
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.34,0:06:20.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,少嘍嗦  靜靜跟著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.68,0:06:23.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你...你這話是什麼意思?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.05,0:06:28.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,從這裏打的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.81,0:06:57.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有沒有見過這個男的?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.81,0:06:59.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不認識
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.41,0:07:02.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他應該是在這附近換新義體的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.98,0:07:04.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,誰知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.48,0:07:09.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這附近幾乎都是以最低限度機能刻苦生活的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.59,0:07:11.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也給我看看吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.09,0:07:16.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,最近很多人失蹤  說不定我認識
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.36,0:07:17.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是這個男子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.60,0:07:19.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.30,0:07:21.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,果然是這傢伙啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.77,0:07:22.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你認識他嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.04,0:07:24.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不認識這傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.77,0:07:27.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過  四、五天前有個在這種大熱天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:27.67,0:07:30.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還穿黑西裝的男人問過我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.41,0:07:32.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有著危險面孔的男人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.01,0:07:38.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且剛剛在人群附近有個年輕小姐也在找同一個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.62,0:07:41.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個帥哥到底幹了什麼好事啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.82,0:07:43.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.36,0:07:44.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,謝謝你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.93,0:07:47.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不好意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.50,0:07:51.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請問你們認識一個叫作古潭完治的人嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.00,0:07:54.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,認識啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.30,0:07:55.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.64,0:07:57.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跟我來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.52,0:08:20.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那種意外的寶貝果然很少見啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.16,0:08:23.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.26,0:08:24.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,托古薩先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.03,0:08:28.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,線
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.27,0:08:33.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好像斷了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.83,0:09:00.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不想挨揍就快滾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.41,0:09:06.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你沒事吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:18.65,0:09:20.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,關於聯絡時提到的男子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.65,0:09:27.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,已確認在關東招慰難民居住區的確有個男的叫古潭完治
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.36,0:09:28.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.39,0:09:32.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我把男子的照片和戒指給暫且納入我保護下的女子看了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:32.40,0:09:35.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她說是古潭的東西沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:35.44,0:09:36.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個女子是什麼人?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.97,0:09:38.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,淺木琉璃子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.47,0:09:42.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,兩年前曾參加援助難民的NG0(非政府組織)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.41,0:09:45.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就在那時候認識了古潭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:46.01,0:09:48.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,後來兩人仍繼續聯絡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:48.85,0:09:52.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,甚至約好有一天要在一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.15,0:09:56.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過  三個月前古潭失去聯絡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.12,0:10:00.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,然後在一個禮拜前突然收到表示要分手的信件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:00.33,0:10:04.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,於是她為了找古潭從秋田來到東京
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:04.40,0:10:05.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.30,0:10:07.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,繼續跟那個女人詢問經過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.50,0:10:08.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,瞭解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:20.98,0:10:22.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,冷靜下來了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:33.59,0:10:35.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,古潭 to 琉璃子 forever
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:35.13,0:10:38.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,古潭已經死了  對吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:39.80,0:10:43.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是古潭送我的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:43.40,0:10:46.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他說很快就能離開難民街了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:48.54,0:10:51.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是想去取得ID的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:51.58,0:10:54.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,古潭的義體卻通不過審查
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:54.11,0:10:57.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為他沒有具備最低限度的性能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:58.08,0:11:00.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道這件事之後  古潭他...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.85,0:11:03.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,開始躲避我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:03.76,0:11:08.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也許是因為他認為我隱瞞了規格
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:08.66,0:11:11.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你沒辦法跟他聯絡上嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:11.23,0:11:12.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,聯絡過好幾次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:13.00,0:11:17.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我還說要幫他取得新的義體
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:17.64,0:11:20.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過  他拒絕了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:20.91,0:11:22.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在新濱被發現的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:22.44,0:11:25.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,古潭已經換上了國產的義體
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.01,0:11:29.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你沒有聽他說過嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:29.28,0:11:31.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒有  沒聽他說過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:31.68,0:11:32.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:39.73,0:11:42.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老實說他在死前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.50,0:11:44.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,涉嫌恐嚇某個國家機關
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.40,0:11:47.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,想要勒索金錢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:48.53,0:11:50.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,聽你說這件事的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:50.14,0:11:54.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我還以為古潭是為了得到義體才想到要去恐嚇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:54.31,0:11:57.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,結果他早就更換過義體了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:57.11,0:11:59.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼在得到義體之後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:59.71,0:12:02.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他還要去犯下恐嚇案件呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:02.12,0:12:05.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,古潭雖然被迫過著懷才不遇的生活
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:05.39,0:12:08.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過  他不是那種會去犯罪的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:08.42,0:12:09.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,或許吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:09.99,0:12:12.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過  古潭的死不是意外
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.86,0:12:15.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有可能是被某個人殺死的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:16.66,0:12:22.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,減少跟你聯絡的那三個月當中他身上一定發生了什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:23.94,0:12:26.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,明天去人多的地方打聽看看吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:36.32,0:12:39.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好像是一個月前吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.12,0:12:44.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,盛傳有個傢伙在大量招用完全義體的勞工
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:44.56,0:12:47.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,聽說只要有意願到「內環七」去工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:47.13,0:12:50.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就免費贈送不錯的義體
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:50.90,0:12:51.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,免費?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:52.00,0:12:53.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.50,0:12:56.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個「內環七」是什麼地方?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.10,0:12:58.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,指沒入水中的那一帶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.60,0:13:02.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是我沒聽說有人真的拿到義體
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:02.08,0:13:05.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那說不定只是謠傳罷了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.05,0:13:09.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個人好像就拿到了新的義體
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.05,0:13:15.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂  有沒有人知道那個可以拿到義體的傳言?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:15.99,0:13:18.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,聽說這個男子真的拿到全身義體
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:19.03,0:13:21.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不知道啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.48,0:13:43.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我現在還活著都是老師的功勞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:44.02,0:13:45.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老師?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:45.52,0:13:50.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在內環七教了我很多事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.99,0:13:53.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在那邊發生了什麼事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:53.29,0:13:54.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也不太清楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:54.96,0:13:58.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只是按照指示工作而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:58.63,0:14:01.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還記得僱主是誰嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:01.10,0:14:04.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,記得叫什麼黑松電設的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:05.00,0:14:09.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,據說是要發掘在戰爭當中被掩埋的設備
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:09.28,0:14:10.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為要進入非常深的地底
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:10.98,0:14:14.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以要我們換成全身義體之後再集合
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:17.92,0:14:23.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,由於條件是義體化比率98％我一度想要放棄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:23.56,0:14:28.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,後來還是請黑市醫生幫我謊報義體化比率混了進去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.43,0:14:31.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那些義體上有這個標誌嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.43,0:14:32.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:33.27,0:14:34.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,全部都有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.54,0:14:41.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老師對能夠換裝新義體感到非常高興
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.97,0:14:44.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,自己又沒辦法看到自己的腦殼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.98,0:14:48.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,誰知道是不是真的拿到新品
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:50.08,0:14:54.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就這樣召集到40個左右的工人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.22,0:14:56.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,進入非常深的地底
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:56.96,0:15:01.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,除了我之外好像也有人謊報了義體化比率
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:01.39,0:15:04.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,後來我跟老師編成一組開始工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:04.80,0:15:07.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,記得他一直說什麼「熱交換管」之類的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:08.37,0:15:10.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖然戴著防塵面具
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:10.37,0:15:12.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還是連鼻子裏面都變黑了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:12.91,0:15:17.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老師說只要切斷感覺器官就沒事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:17.28,0:15:20.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我說我不是全身義體無法切斷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:20.85,0:15:24.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,結果老師的表情變得非常可怕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.08,0:15:27.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他說如果不馬上離開這裏我一定會死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.52,0:15:30.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是  我無論如何都需要那筆錢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:30.82,0:15:32.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以沒聽老師的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:33.13,0:15:37.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,於是老師拿這個給我並且說要是這個變成黑色
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:37.50,0:15:39.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就要趕快逃出去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:40.87,0:15:45.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,然後在開工之後的第四天發生了嚴重的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:46.84,0:15:48.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,突然警報大作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:48.51,0:15:51.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,心裏還在想出了什麼事的時候從裏面的工作現場
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:51.11,0:15:55.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有一群像是技術人員的人躺在擔架上被抬了出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:57.35,0:15:58.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如此一來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:58.78,0:16:01.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我終於明白這個工作有多危險
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:03.79,0:16:05.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因此逃了出來?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:05.99,0:16:07.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.83,0:16:12.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,回過神來才發現有群身穿黑衣的人跑了進來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:13.10,0:16:16.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我和老師雖然順利逃到外面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:16.97,0:16:19.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過  逃命過程中回頭一看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:19.91,0:16:25.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,發現一起去的同伴都被關在巨大的鐵門後面了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:26.71,0:16:29.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在那之後  古潭他怎麼了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:29.72,0:16:35.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他說一定要把自己在隧道裏看到的事情公諸於世
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.92,0:16:37.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就不知道去哪裏了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:42.93,0:16:46.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可以帶我們到內環七去嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:46.17,0:16:47.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別說傻話了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:47.37,0:16:50.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就算給錢我也不回那種鬼地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:50.34,0:16:52.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只帶到半路也沒關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:52.07,0:16:53.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,求求你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:53.37,0:16:57.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也想知道古潭在那裏看到了什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:11.12,0:17:12.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,陸上自衛軍已經到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:13.16,0:17:16.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我逃出來的時候還沒有那道鐵絲網
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:22.77,0:17:25.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,從這裏進去就能到同一個地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:25.87,0:17:28.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不好意思  我只能帶到這裏為止
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:28.34,0:17:29.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:29.14,0:17:30.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,謝謝你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:20.39,0:18:21.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:27.57,0:18:28.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,武裝機甲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:53.89,0:18:54.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:58.23,0:18:59.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快跳過來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:02.70,0:19:03.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:46.01,0:20:47.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你沒事吧  托古薩先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:48.11,0:20:49.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,塔奇克馬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:13.70,0:21:18.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到站的列車是往新福岡的未來52號
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:18.37,0:21:20.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,古潭為了跟你在一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:20.57,0:21:23.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,明知有危險還是到那裏去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:23.64,0:21:28.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,剛好又有足夠知識知道那裏是什麼設施
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:28.35,0:21:29.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以才會被殺害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:30.95,0:21:34.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我先回家一趟就去接古潭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:35.35,0:21:37.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有事請馬上跟我聯絡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:37.92,0:21:38.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:49.13,0:21:53.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,古潭在埋藏於深度地底的核電廠中碰到那件事故
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:53.27,0:21:56.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就以此事來恐嚇能源省
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:56.24,0:22:00.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過 他這麼做也有可能是想把這件醜聞公諸於世
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:00.31,0:22:02.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:02.28,0:22:05.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,據推測應該是在作業當中發生臨界事故
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:06.02,0:22:08.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,然後急忙將其掩埋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:08.95,0:22:11.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,軍方好像也沒有掌握到實際狀況
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:11.76,0:22:18.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,問題在於想要挖出戰前遺物的人到底隸屬哪裏管轄 有什麼目的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:18.43,0:22:20.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個穿黑西裝的
